companyName: U.S. Equity Cumulative Dividends Fund Series 2027 Shares
description:
The investment seeks to provide monthly payments that replicate the cash dividends paid by component companies in the S&P 500®️ Index, without price exposure to these underlying stocks, as represented by the Solactive US Cumulative Dividends Index - Series 2027.
The manager intends to track the performance of the Solactive Dividend Index by owning U.S. Treasury securities and long positions in annual S&P 500 Dividend Futures Contracts out to the maturity date of the fund.
